The paper discusses the use of modern cryptography techniques for securing data in cloud computing, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of virtualized resources and distributed networks, which are common topics in distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). The use of encryption algorithms also falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of data security in cloud computing, which is a topic in cyber security (cs.CY).
